# Input

```graphql
query ($storyId: ID!, $like: Boolean,

	$comments: [String!], $tags: [String!]!,

	$posts: [PostInput]!, $input: [input!]!

) {


	likeStory(storyId: $storyId)
}


```


# Formatted

```graphql
query (
	$storyId: ID!
	$like: Boolean
	$comments: [String!]
	$tags: [String!]!
	$posts: [PostInput]!
	$input: [input!]!
) {
	likeStory(storyId: $storyId)
}

```
